Class Table

  • java.lang.Object
    • CZ2002_assignment.Table
  • public class Table
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a Table A Table can be of three different sizes depending on the number of people it can accomodate A Table can have one of the three status at one time : Vacant, Occupied or Reserved
